Description: A Taste Of The ActionLocated in the casino's race & sports book, the Sports Book Grill is a great place to eat when you are in a rush, or just want a tasty sandwich, burger or salad while watching the game. (You must be 21 years of age or older to enter the Sports Book Grill.)
Location: 3950 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89119
